item.title: WaiWai Check 8/26 (English)
item.description: WaiWai Check 8/26 (わいわいチェック 8/26) is a Satellaview game. The ROM was originally dumped through the effort of several people and published on the Satellablog. Roms (Japanese and English) Japanese ROM English Patch On Satellablog ROM CRC32: 729F0D04 Download Wai Wai Check (8-26) (English).bps The game The game is a “spot the difference” game. You have an animated image on the left and the mirrored version on the right with 5 differences.
